store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231990/extras/bfdba81adbb1040489f5e9d462503768.webm?t=1770711179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231990/extras/bfdba81adbb1040489f5e9d462503768.mp4?t=1770711179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的场地/环境/球变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231990/extras/a93cd563fbf0adef456ca44aabcc1a93.poster.avif?t=1770711179\" width=450 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231990/extras/a93cd563fbf0adef456ca44aabcc1a93.webm?t=1770711179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231990/extras/a93cd563fbf0adef456ca44aabcc1a93.mp4?t=1770711179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特别鸣谢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>CandyWind, Vescrity, Rolone, LeafSong, PakchoL, Jamesika, Xue.🥳, Lanchen, Lilac, Wtchen</i></p>",
